reviewText: I love the double feature style.....both movies played perfectly.  Two movies in one package saves storage space.
Great movie combination.  Lots of action, interlaced with good humor.
was a gift that made someone very happy.
Got this mainly for Rio Bravo.  No one is better in westerns than John Wayne.
These are two of the best westerns ever made!
Love, love this movie. How could you go wrong with dean Martin, Rickey Nelson, Walter Brennan, and Ward Bond, and of course the Great John Wayne. Good story, Great acting.
2 of the best westerns ever made.
John made a name for grand acting, and grand living. Hollywood exploited him in every way possible, but John still won.
